{
  "texts": [
    "OpportunitiesAmong all the included papers, few of them propose solutions to improve the reliability of LLMs.",
    "First, future research work should focus more on how to improve the accuracy of LLMs' responses in the healthcare domain.",
    "More specifically, domain-specific health data are demanded for training and finetuning of LLMs to improve the performance of LLMs in various tasks in the healthcare domain.",
    "Therefore, data harmonization and consortia established for LLM training are potential directions that can benefit the broad research community.",
    "Qualified medical professionals can contribute to the creation of the dataset for LLM training."
  ]
}